videos.description: Texas A&M's Tyler Davis uses a nice post move and punishes the rim.
videos.headline: Davis throws it down with authority

videos.description: Jay Jay Chandler drives hard on the baseline and finishes with a saucy reverse layup.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Chandler goes up and under the hoop

videos.description: Admon Gilder lays it in as he takes the foul and falls to the floor to beat the shot clock.
videos.headline: Gilder completes and-1 for Aggies

videos.description: D.J. Hogg nails the three and gets a chance for a four-point play as the Aggies extend their lead.
videos.headline: Hogg hits three and draws a foul
